last_episode_to_air.name: Glee Reunion Battle & Jason Biggs vs. Eddie Kaye Thomas
last_episode_to_air.overview: Glee" stars Amber Riley, Harry Shum Jr. and Becca Tobin battle former castmates Kevin McHale, Jenna Ushkowitz and Heather Morris; Jason Biggs and Eddie Kaye Thomas of "American Pie" serve up slices of lyrical hurt.

name: Drop the Mic
overview: Based on a popular segment on "The Late Late Show With James Corden" and emceed by rapper-actor Method Man and model Hailey Baldwin, "Drop the Mic" invites celebrities from the worlds of entertainment, music, sports, and pop culture to compete in rap battles. Episodes feature four players in head-to-head battles, creating moments packed with lyrical creativity and "Did you hear that?" moments. Studio audience votes determine the mic-dropping winner of each battle.

episodes.name: Halle Berry vs. James Corden & Usher vs. Anthony Anderson
episodes.overview: James Corden takes on Halle Berry and Usher faces funnyman Anthony Anderson in a lyrical duel. No matter who wins - it's gonna get personal.

episodes.name: James Van Der Beek vs. Randall Park & Rob Gronkowski vs. Gina Rodriguez
episodes.overview: Dawson's Creek heartthrob James Van Der Beek throws shade at Fresh off the Boat's Randall Park in a rap battle, while NFL superstar and Super Bowl champ Rob Gronkowski finds out Gina Rodriguez might just be a problem he can't tackle.

episodes.name: Niecy Nash vs. Cedric the Entertainer & Liam Payne vs. Jason Derulo
episodes.overview: Niecy Nash lets the Claws come out when she faces Cedric the Entertainer, while music industry giants Jason Derulo & One Direction's Liam Payne rap battle for the pop music crown.

episodes.name: Tony Hale Vs. Timothy Simons & Rascal Flatts Vs. Boyz II Men
Nicole Scherzinger vs. Lil Rel Howery and Charlie Puth vs. Backstreet Boys
Vanessa Hudgens Vs. Michael Bennett And James Corden Vs. Nicole Richie
Mayim Bialik vs. Kunal Nayyar; Ashley Tisdale vs. Nick Lachey
Wayne Brady vs. Jake Owen; Kenny G. vs. Richard Marx
David Arquette vs. Brian Tyree Henry; Jesse Tyler Ferguson vs. Chrissy Metz
Pentatonix vs. Bell Biv Devoe; Padma Lakshmi vs. Randy Jackson
episodes.overview: Grammy winners Pentatonix lyrically battle '90s pioneers Bell Biv Devoe; ``Top Chef'''s Padma Lakshmi and ``American Idol'''s Randy Jackson see which host has the hottest bars.

episodes.name: Danielle Fishel vs. Jonathan Lipnicki; Shania Twain vs. Meghan Trainor
Shaquille O'Neal vs. Ken Jeong and Jerry Springer vs. Ricki Lake
episodes.overview: Drop The Mic is back with the hottest (and only) celebrity rap battles! Season 2 kicks off with a David & Goliath, when Shaquille O' Neal trades barbs with comedian Ken Jeong, and we see which talk show host can REALLY work the mic when Ricki Lake goes head-to-head with Jerry Springer in a classic heavyweight match.

episodes.name: Shawn Mendes vs. Odell Beckham Jr. & Molly Ringwald vs. Jon Cryer
episodes.overview: Pop sensation Shawn Mendes tries to stop the forward progress of football star Odell Beckham Jr. when it comes to lyrical warfare; when "Pretty in Pink" co-stars Molly Ringwald and Jon Cryer spit Brat Pack bars to see who will reign supreme.

episodes.name: Seth Rogen vs. Joseph Gordon-Levitt & Terry Crews vs. Luis Fonsi
episodes.overview: Seth Rogen vs. Joseph Gordon-Levitt & Terry Crews vs. Luis Fonsi

episodes.name: Marlon Wayans vs. Jay Pharoah & Lindsey Vonn vs. Gus Kenworthy
episodes.overview: Marlon Wayans battles Jay Pharoah in a war that cannot be erased; and an All-American showdown between Lindsey Vonn and Gus Kenworthy will leave only one rapper on the slopes.

episodes.name: Darren Criss vs. Gaten Matarazzo & Chandler Riggs vs. Chad L. Coleman
episodes.overview: Darren Criss ("American Crime Story") vs. Gaten Matarazzo ("Stranger Things"); and two former "Walking Dead" stars, Chandler Riggs and Chad L. Coleman, battle it out.

episodes.name: Taye Diggs vs Karrueche Tran and Jodie Sweetin vs Mark McGrath
episodes.overview: Taye Diggs and Karrueche Tran will spill all the tea when they go head-to-head. Also: Sugar Ray lead singer Mark McGrath tries to catch Jodie Sweetin ("Full House") slipping.

episodes.name: Hanson vs. Sam Richardson & Shaggy vs. Matthew Lillard
episodes.overview: The loveable brothers of Hanson enter the savage battlegrounds to face Sam Richardson ("Veep"). And it's a duel of Shaggys when Matthew Lillard ("Scooby-Doo") is the underdog when paired against musician Shaggy.

episodes.name: Michael K. Williams vs. Trevor Jackson; James Corden vs. Dr. Phil
episodes.overview: Michael K. Williams battles Trevor Jackson; James Corden puts his losing streak on the line against a man whose name is synonymous with rap battles: Dr. Phil.

episodes.name: WWE Superstars vs. GLOW & Chris Jericho vs. Laila Ali
episodes.overview: WWE Superstars Nikki & Brie Bella, Alicia Fox & Carmella face the stars of GLOW Kate Nash, Jackie Tohn, Britney Young & Sunita Mani. While the Ayatollah of Rock 'n' Rolla, Chris Jericho, has his hands full with an undefeated, Laila Ali.

episodes.name: Luis Guzman vs. Gabriel Iglesias & Charli XCX vs. Tove Lo
episodes.overview: Actor Luis Guzman has one of the most extensive resumes in Hollywood, but can he rap battle?

episodes.name: Taran Killam vs. Rob Riggle and Boy George vs. Laverne Cox
episodes.overview: SNL alums Taran Killam and Rob Riggle face off in an epic battle; LGBTQ icons past and present collide as Culture Clubs Boy George faces off with Orange Is the New Black star Laverne Cox.

episodes.name: The Muppets Matchup and Lost Reunion Battle
episodes.overview: Kermit and Pepe go up against Miss Piggy and Beaker in the greatest (and only) Muppet rap battle of all time; three castaways from Lost, Daniel Dae Kim, Josh Holloway and Harold Perrineau, have a not-so-friendly mainland reunion.

episodes.name: Kat Graham vs. Shameik Moore and Nikki Glaser vs. Brad Williams
episodes.overview: The Vampire Diaries star Kat Graham takes a bite out of Shameik Moore. Can this Spider-Man fight back? Then it's a standup standoff when two comedy giants, Nikki Glaser and Brad Williams, start throwing punch lines.

episodes.name: Lonzo Ball vs. T-pain and Kevin Smith vs. Jason Mewes
episodes.overview: Basketball star Lonzo Ball tries to dunk on the king of auto-tune, T-Pain; friends become foes as a slimmed-down Kevin Smith goes head to head with Jason Mewes; Jay and Silent Bob will never be the same.

episodes.name: Mike Colter vs. Ne-yo and Christina Milian vs. Ashlee Simpson
episodes.overview: Drop The Mic is at Universal Orlando Resort in Orlando, FL. R&B singer NE-YO battles Mike Colter to see if he's as tough as Luke Cage. Then it's a pop star party when Christina Milian and Ashlee Simpson see which voice can deal more pain.

episodes.name: Jack Osbourne vs. Kelly Osbourne and Mel B vs. La La Anthony
episodes.overview: DTM leaves Universal Orlando Resort with a bang! Jack and Kelly Osbourne take sibling rivalry to the next level in a family feud rap battle. Then Spice Girl Mel B spars with La La Anthony when there's only room for one diva on stage.

episodes.name: Ron Funches vs. Raven-Symone and Joey Fatone vs. Joey McIntyre
episodes.overview: Funnyman Ron Funches battles Raven-Symone, who may look harmless, but is a beast with the mic. Then it's a battle of boy band legends with NSync's Joey Fatone and NKOTB's Joey McIntrye pushing their friendship aside to go one-on-one.

episodes.name: Jason Mitchell vs. Adina Porter & David Faustino vs. Joey Lawrence
episodes.overview: Straight Outta Compton's Jason Mitchell channels Eazy-E against American Horror Story's chilling Adina Porter. Then 90's TV teens are grown up as Married With Children's David Faustino and Blossom's Joey Lawrence duke it out with bars.

episodes.name: Mark Cuban vs. Rusev & Lana & The New Day vs. SWV
episodes.overview: Wrestling superstars Rusev and Lana hunt shark Mark Cuban to see who's the baddest beast; tag-team champs The New Day jump in the ring with iconic soul singers SWV in a no-holds-barred grudge match.
